  "1725410": {
    "name": "Talespinner",
    "steam_appid": 1725410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/cb5164b235d4c0f2fa400ab9e72351ce.avif?t=1765210971\" width=800 height=258 /></span>踏入一个浸染在光怪陆离的日本神话中的迷人领域！《织语者》是一款牌组构筑类Roguelike冒险游戏。作为说书人，你将引导你选择的英雄，在一个由你的决策与牌组构筑所塑造的、不断变幻的叙事中前行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/6bdc1c0264ac33f68e40bf606b6fd6c4.webp?t=1765210971\" width=240 height=29 /></span><br><br>选择你的英雄<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/e15f00cac437ec33fb59d3e3c9aaf1a9.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/e15f00cac437ec33fb59d3e3c9aaf1a9.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/e15f00cac437ec33fb59d3e3c9aaf1a9.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每个故事都需要一位英雄。从3位独特的角色中挑选，他们各自拥有截然不同的游戏机制与一套可随游戏进程升级的强大卡牌组。锻造强大的卡牌协同效应，主宰整个叙事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/38dd33d7f33c3d075360a931ae27186b.webp?t=1765210971\" width=288 height=29 /></span><br><br>挑选你的剧本<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/d26bb076325d7f151523676c5338befb.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/d26bb076325d7f151523676c5338befb.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/d26bb076325d7f151523676c5338befb.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>决定你的英雄将踏上何种冒险。正被著名的服部半藏所率领的忍者集团追杀？还是选择深入群山，追踪在当地作祟的雪女？<br><br>每个剧本都提供多处故事转折，增添层层挑战与重复可玩性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/3c668e2d9fa0aa20e23c156ca82f5492.webp?t=1765210971\" width=258 height=29 /></span><br><br>执笔你的道路<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/ae78601b5af7b2657e73db952bcc9141.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/ae78601b5af7b2657e73db952bcc9141.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/ae78601b5af7b2657e73db952bcc9141.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用你的故事书来决定英雄的遭遇。随心所欲调整挑战难度，或降低难度以推进故事，或提高风险以博取更丰厚的奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/0e1962645b96f69da2987328d32b5a67.webp?t=1765210971\" width=370 height=30 /></span><br><br>遭遇百鬼妖异<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/b71f8f06983bf91b995afc4e0dbff4c2.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/b71f8f06983bf91b995afc4e0dbff4c2.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/b71f8f06983bf91b995afc4e0dbff4c2.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沉浸于源自日本神话的妖异世界。每种妖怪都拥有一套迥异的技能，让每一次遭遇都成为独特的挑战。如何应对它们，全由你定夺：是在决绝的战斗中将它们斩落，还是凭借魅力与巧智化敌为友？ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/e17b99b840a4eb8053e0ecd82d0ca226.webp?t=1765210971\" width=461 height=30 /></span><br><br>直面邪恶强敌<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/6f4dc13f66e657070d84d24502f1cc24.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/6f4dc13f66e657070d84d24502f1cc24.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/6f4dc13f66e657070d84d24502f1cc24.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在战斗中对抗各式敌对势力，它们能影响你英雄卡牌的效果，从而增强沉浸感，并随着遭遇更多不同对手来发掘战斗的策略深度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/cf64156c54a08025f9e0d86b7a5cf6e6.webp?t=1765210971\" width=571 height=30 /></span><br><br>游历奇景异域<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/f4971237355dc16de65dd4d2497039d6.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/f4971237355dc16de65dd4d2497039d6.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/f4971237355dc16de65dd4d2497039d6.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>开启一场史诗之旅，穿梭于诸如竹林、神秘洞穴、风之平原、诅咒村落、古老神殿等多种生态区域。每个区域都提供多样的事件以及独特的敌人组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/8ff6c5cb30cc831df1aceb970c3db971.poster.avif?t=1765210971\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/8ff6c5cb30cc831df1aceb970c3db971.webm?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/8ff6c5cb30cc831df1aceb970c3db971.mp4?t=1765210971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725410/extras/b5822a15305dd1939d6d7be42204fb4d.webp?t=1765210971\" width=231 height=30 /></span><br><br>主要特色</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三大可玩角色，拥有独特机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200余张战斗卡牌，供你收集与升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3个基于日本神话的独特剧本，内含可解锁的故事分支</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50多种形态各异的敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16位极具挑战的首领</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8处氛围独特的生态区域</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30多个独特的随机事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50多位战术助力伙伴</p></li></ul>",
